  "text": "First, I show how the presence of information asymmetry about abatement costs may exacerbate the free-rider problem. [CITATION_1] The second contribution of this paper is the introduction of a communication stage during which countries have the possibility to exchange verifiable information trough an international agency. In doing so, I also propose a new channel to restore the feasibility of an efficient agreement:",
